Subject: [Accel-config] [PATCH v1 2/2] accel-config: Fix batch event log
	core check output issues
X-BeenThere: accel-config@lists.linuxfoundation.org
X-Mailman-Version: 2.1.15
Precedence: list
List-Id: accel-config <accel-config.lists.linuxfoundation.org>
